  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Grill the French bread until charred, flipping halfway through.",
    "3. Let the bread cool completely, then cube it.",
    "4. In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens, blackberries, and chopped mint leaves.",
    "5. Drizzle the balsamic vinaigrette over the salad and toss to coat.",
    "6. Add the cubed French bread to the salad and toss gently to combine.",
    "7. If using feta cheese, crumble it over the salad and toss to combine.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
